SystemsToSpawn: List of all the systems we want to spawn.
TimeBetweenSpawns: The time delay we should use between spawning if we have a list to spawn.
bKillBeforeSpawn: Should we kill systems we spawn before we spawn another.
bWorldLocation: When true the location is a world location, when false it's relative to the player and is in camera space.
Location: The location we should use to spawn the system at, either world or local to the player depending on WorldLocation flag.
bAttachToPlayer: Should we attach to the player controlled by the camera or not
bAutoActivate: Should we auto activate or not
bAutoDestroy: Should we auto destroy when complete or not
bDoPreCullCheck: Should we perform the pre cull check or not
